<h3>How many pounds in a gram</h3>
<p>There are 0.00220462 pounds in 1 gram.</p>
<h3>How many grams in a pound</h3>
<p>There are 453.59237 grams in 1 pound.</p>
<h2>How to convert pounds to grams</h2>
<p>To convert from grams to pounds multiply or divide by the appropriate co=
nversion factors shown below.</p>
